average Autobots.  It was our favorite past time, ta do research, and look 
up ancient records and artifacts.  Well, in one of those articles, I found 
something about powerlinking.  And what I read, it stated that because 
Autobots are so well in tuned with each other, and that their bond of unity 
is unbroken by anyone, it&#39;s their faith in each other, that gives them the 
