spiritual faith in each other, a bond that no one can break, and I know that 
when Tucson went looking for you Rodimus, he went looking for you with all 
his heart.  The power to do the extraordinary, lies within your heart.  I 
know you have it, you just have to believe in yourself, listen to your 
heart, and have faith in those who have faith in you.&quot;

